cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to understand and annotate song lyrics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval and machine translation, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) respectively. The use of machine learning models for performance evaluation suggests cs.LG (Learning) as another possible category. Finally, the paper deals with crowdsourcing, which could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
